# Zoho Mail Skill

## What this skill does

| Feature | Description |
|---|---|
| `check_inbox` | รายการเมลเข้าล่าสุด (inbox) |
| `check_sent` | รายการเมลออกล่าสุด (sent) |
| `read_email` | อ่านเนื้อหาเมลเต็ม |
| `search_email` | ค้นหาเมลด้วย keyword |
| `check_storage` | ตรวจสอบพื้นที่ใช้งาน / แจ้งเตือนเมื่อใกล้เต็ม |
| `backup_emails` | สำรองข้อมูลเมลเป็นไฟล์ JSONL |

## Setup (one-time)

```bash
# 1. Install dependencies
pip install -r requirements.txt

# 2. Create .env from template
cp .env.example .env
# Fill in ZOHO_CLIENT_ID, ZOHO_CLIENT_SECRET, ZOHO_REFRESH_TOKEN, ZOHO_ACCOUNT_EMAIL

# 3. Get OAuth2 credentials from https://api-console.zoho.com/
#    - Create a "Self Client"
#    - Scope: ZohoMail.messages.READ, ZohoMail.accounts.READ
#    - Generate refresh token via Authorization Code flow
```

## Claude Code setup

Add to `.claude/settings.json`:
```json
{
  "mcpServers": {
    "zoho-mail": {
      "command": "python",
      "args": ["D:/zoho-mail/mcp_server.py"],
      "env": {
        "ZOHO_CLIENT_ID": "...",
        "ZOHO_CLIENT_SECRET": "...",
        "ZOHO_REFRESH_TOKEN": "...",
        "ZOHO_ACCOUNT_EMAIL": "you@domain.com"
      }
    }
  }
}
```

## ChatGPT / OpenAI Codex setup

```python
import openai, json
from openai_dispatcher import dispatch

tools = json.load(open("openai_tools.json"))

messages = [{"role": "user", "content": "Check my inbox"}]
while True:
    resp = openai.chat.completions.create(
        model="gpt-4o", messages=messages,
        tools=tools, tool_choice="auto",
    )
    msg = resp.choices[0].message
    if not msg.tool_calls:
        print(msg.content); break
    messages.append(msg)
    for tc in msg.tool_calls:
        result = dispatch(tc.function.name, json.loads(tc.function.arguments))
        messages.append({
            "role": "tool", "tool_call_id": tc.id,
            "content": json.dumps(result, ensure_ascii=False),
        })
```

## Continuous monitoring

```bash
# Poll inbox + storage every 60 seconds (default)
python monitor.py

# Custom interval (seconds)
POLL_SECONDS=30 python monitor.py
```

## Backup

```bash
# Via Python
python -c "import zoho_client as z; print(z.backup_folder('Inbox', 1000))"

# Or ask Claude / ChatGPT:
# "Backup my inbox, up to 200 messages"
```

## Example prompts (Claude or ChatGPT)

- "ตรวจสอบเมลเข้าใหม่ 10 ฉบับล่าสุด"
- "พื้นที่อีเมลใช้ไปแล้วเท่าไร ใกล้เต็มไหม"
- "ค้นหาเมลจาก noreply@github.com"
- "Backup กล่อง Inbox ไว้ก่อนเลย 500 ฉบับ"
- "Show me sent emails from this week"

## File layout

```
zoho-mail/
├── .env.example          # Environment variable template
├── requirements.txt      # Python dependencies
├── zoho_client.py        # Zoho API client (shared core)
├── mcp_server.py         # Claude Code MCP server
├── openai_tools.json     # ChatGPT/Codex tool definitions
├── openai_dispatcher.py  # ChatGPT function call dispatcher
├── monitor.py            # Standalone continuous monitor
└── zoho-mail.skill       # This skill file
```
